summary: Completed comprehensive testing of RentEase rental marketplace platform. Backend APIs working excellently (8/9 tests passed). Frontend UI loads well but has form validation issues preventing complete user registration flow.

minor_issues.issue: Returns 520 Cloudflare error instead of 500 for invalid MongoDB ObjectId
minor_issues.impact: Minor - expected behavior in cloud environment

ui_bugs.issue: Form validation inconsistent - name field validation fails even when properly filled

integration_issues.issue: Frontend registration form not properly submitting to backend API despite form being filled

passed_tests: API health check returns correct message
Homepage loads with search bar and quick filters
Navigation links (Browse, Login, Sign Up) present and functional
Protected routes working (listings redirects to login)
Registration form UI displays correctly with role selection
Backend user registration API (Customer & Owner roles)

success_percentage.frontend: 70% (UI loads well, navigation works, but form submission fails)

action_item_for_main_agent: Fix registration form validation and submission logic - form validation is preventing successful user registration despite all fields being filled correctly. The backend API works fine, but frontend form handling has issues.
